{"type":"message","id":"cd311b8d","parentId":"056fe82a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T09:49:27.856Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01Q5OHDcNVUjFkLY2pDBMJzy","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# wechat-article\n\n读取微信公众号文章内容。\n\n## 何时使用\n\n当用户需要：\n- 读取微信公众号文章\n- 分析公众号内容\n- 提取文章信息\n\n## 工具\n\n`wechat-article <url>` - 读取公众号文章\n\n## 返回格式\n\nJSON格式：\n```json\n{\n  \"title\": \"文章标题\",\n  \"author\": \"作者/公众号名称\",\n  \"content\": \"正文内容（纯文本）\"\n}\n```\n\n## 使用示例\n\n```bash\nwechat-article https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/xxxxx\n```\n\n## 实现方式\n\n使用requests + BeautifulSoup直接解析HTML，无需浏览器驱动，速度快。\n\n## 创建者\n\nRainbow - 2026-03-13\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773827367855}}
