{"type":"message","id":"9d6dc992","parentId":"aa6de946","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:23:03.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你说的授权码具体是指什么？\n\n- OpenClaw 的授权码？\n- 飞书的授权配置？\n- 邮箱的授权码？\n- 还是其他服务的 API key？\n\n说清楚点，我好帮你找。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":87,"output":74,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":54090,"totalTokens":54251,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773836575947}}
{"type":"message","id":"bf8b87e9","parentId":"9d6dc992","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:23:48.793Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b549ddbf2f4b0c11e31f26d25ff0\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户248287\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 20:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户248287 (ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\",\n  \"name\": \"用户248287\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b549ddbf2f4b0c11e31f26d25ff0]\n用户248287: 但是授权码在哪里？我找不到"}],"timestamp":1773836628791}}
{"type":"message","id":"0c1cd27d","parentId":"bf8b87e9","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:23:56.922Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"你还是没说清楚是什么授权码。\n\n不过既然你在用 OpenClaw 和飞书，我猜你可能是在找：\n\n**飞书应用的配置信息**（App ID / App Secret）：\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/config.json | grep -A 10 feishu\n```\n\n**OpenClaw 的 API keys**（如果配置了模型）：\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/config.json | grep -i \"key\\|token\\|secret\"\n```\n\n要不你直接告诉我你想干什么，我帮你定位具体位置？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":87,"output":170,"cacheRead":54090,"cacheWrite":335,"totalTokens":54682,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773836628792}}
{"type":"message","id":"4fdd9f65","parentId":"0c1cd27d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:24:27.274Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b549dd96588acc4c0bc01e4e9ee3\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户248287\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 20:24 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户248287 (ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\",\n  \"name\": \"用户248287\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b549dd96588acc4c0bc01e4e9ee3]\n用户248287: 不是你问我邮箱和授权码，但是我不知道邮箱的授权码在什么地方能拿到，不是要找了发给你吗？"}],"timestamp":1773836667272}}
{"type":"message","id":"d63cea9a","parentId":"4fdd9f65","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:24:41.173Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了，你是在找邮箱的授权码。\n\n邮箱授权码不在你电脑上，需要去邮箱服务商那里生成。具体位置取决于你用的是哪家邮箱：\n\n**QQ邮箱：**\n1. 登录 QQ 邮箱网页版\n2. 设置 → 账户 → POP3/IMAP/SMTP/Exchange/CardDAV/CalDAV服务\n3. 开启 IMAP/SMTP 服务\n4. 生成授权码\n\n**163/126邮箱：**\n1. 登录网易邮箱\n2. 设置 → POP3/SMTP/IMAP\n3. 开启服务并生成授权码\n\n**Gmail：**\n1. Google 账户设置\n2. 安全性 → 两步验证（必须先开启）\n3. 应用专用密码\n\n**企业邮箱：**\n看具体是哪家的，一般在邮箱设置里找\"授权码\"或\"应用密码\"。\n\n你用的是哪个邮箱？我给你具体步骤。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":36,"output":283,"cacheRead":54425,"cacheWrite":508,"totalTokens":55252,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773836667273}}
{"type":"message","id":"f0ee65de","parentId":"d63cea9a","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:28:27.123Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b549de86eaca8c142bc4787d5c00\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\",\n  \"sender\": \"用户248287\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-03-18 20:28 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"用户248287 (ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\",\n  \"name\": \"用户248287\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b549de86eaca8c142bc4787d5c00]\n用户248287: 是QQ邮箱"}],"timestamp":1773836907119}}
{"type":"message","id":"accec525","parentId":"f0ee65de","timestamp":"2026-03-18T12:28:36.612Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"QQ邮箱授权码获取步骤：\n\n1. 打开浏览器，访问 https://mail.qq.com\n2. 登录你的QQ邮箱\n3. 点击顶部的\"设置\"\n4. 选择\"账户\"标签\n5. 找到\"POP3/IMAP/SMTP/Exchange/CardDAV/CalDAV服务\"这一栏\n6. 开启\"IMAP/SMTP服务\"（如果还没开）\n7. 点击\"生成授权码\"\n8. 按提示用手机QQ扫码验证\n9. 验证后会显示一串授权码，复制保存\n\n授权码格式一般是16位字母，类似：`abcdefghijklmnop`\n\n拿到后发给我，我帮你配置。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":82,"output":210,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":55410,"totalTokens":55702,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773836907121}}
