{"type":"message","id":"745c9490","parentId":"9b9c59f0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:53:44.640Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"已经有一个定时任务了，每天 22:03 执行。和你要求的时间一致，不需要重复设置。\n\n看看这个脚本是干什么的："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01SfyPqFVwIE3rlM3nvPmC6e","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/cheche/.openclaw/workspace/bot2-import/scripts/daily-report.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":24,"output":77,"cacheRead":63308,"cacheWrite":217,"totalTokens":63626,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773845618255}}
{"type":"message","id":"da923f1c","parentId":"745c9490","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:53:44.646Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01SfyPqFVwIE3rlM3nvPmC6e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/bin/bash\n# 每日日报生成脚本\n\nDATE=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nMEMORY_FILE=\"$HOME/.openclaw/workspace/bot2-import/memory/$DATE.md\"\n\n# 发送日报提醒\necho \"提醒：该写今天的日报了！\" | openclaw --profile bot2 send --channel feishu --user ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\n\n# 如果有今天的 memory 文件，提取关键信息\nif [ -f \"$MEMORY_FILE\" ]; then\n    echo \"今天的工作记录：\" | openclaw --profile bot2 send --channel feishu --user ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\n    cat \"$MEMORY_FILE\" | openclaw --profile bot2 send --channel feishu --user ou_e40c5df02fc12d4786a84a078a9b180d\nfi\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773845624645}}
{"type":"message","id":"cad58e7c","parentId":"da923f1c","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:53:52.544Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"这个脚本是 bot2 的日报提醒，不是我的。时间是 22:03，会发送日报提醒给你。\n\n如果你想让我（Sunny）也在 22:03 发日报，需要单独设置。要加吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":24,"output":81,"cacheRead":63525,"cacheWrite":514,"totalTokens":64144,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773845624648}}
