{"type":"message","id":"d27db804","parentId":"d0fdd91d","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:54:20.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"看看中文的 cron 文档："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_0140kjG2M4MOgLDmlt95d26r","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/cheche/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/automation/cron-jobs.md","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":65,"output":62,"cacheRead":64894,"cacheWrite":488,"totalTokens":65509,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773845654650}}
{"type":"message","id":"f13dba31","parentId":"d27db804","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:54:20.854Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_0140kjG2M4MOgLDmlt95d26r","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nread_when:\n  - 调度后台任务或唤醒\n  - 配置需要与心跳一起或并行运行的自动化\n  - 在心跳和定时任务之间做选择\nsummary: Gateway网关调度器的定时任务与唤醒\ntitle: 定时任务\nx-i18n:\n  generated_at: \"2026-02-01T19:37:32Z\"\n  model: claude-opus-4-5\n  provider: pi\n  source_hash: d43268b0029f1b13d0825ddcc9c06a354987ea17ce02f3b5428a9c68bf936676\n  source_path: automation/cron-jobs.md\n  workflow: 14\n---\n\n# 定时任务（Gateway网关调度器）\n\n> **定时任务还是心跳？** 请参阅[定时任务与心跳对比](/automation/cron-vs-heartbeat)了解何时使用哪种方式。\n\n定时任务是 Gateway网关内置的调度器。它持久化任务、在合适的时间唤醒智能体，并可选择将输出发送回聊天。\n\n如果你想要 _\"每天早上运行\"_ 或 _\"20 分钟后提醒智能体\"_，定时任务就是对应的机制。\n\n## 简要概述\n\n- 定时任务运行在 **Gateway网关内部**（而非模型内部）。\n- 任务持久化存储在 `~/.openclaw/cron/` 下，因此重启不会丢失计划。\n- 两种执行方式：\n  - **主会话**：入队一个系统事件，然后在下一次心跳时运行。\n  - **隔离式**：在 `cron:<jobId>` 中运行专用智能体轮次，可投递摘要（默认 announce）或不投递。\n- 唤醒是一等功能：任务可以请求\"立即唤醒\"或\"下次心跳时\"。\n\n## 快速开始（可操作）\n\n创建一个一次性提醒，验证其存在，然后立即运行：\n\n```bash\nopenclaw cron add \\\n  --name \"Reminder\" \\\n  --at \"2026-02-01T16:00:00Z\" \\\n  --session main \\\n  --system-event \"Reminder: check the cron docs draft\" \\\n  --wake now \\\n  --delete-after-run\n\nopenclaw cron list\nopenclaw cron run <job-id> --force\nopenclaw cron runs --id <job-id>\n```\n\n[375 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773845660853}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a94d10a","parentId":"f13dba31","timestamp":"2026-03-18T14:54:27.033Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了。OpenClaw 有内置的 cron 系统。给你设置每天 22:03 发日报："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"toolu_01taQRQ4Ru21wDap03qIfN7z","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --name \"Sunny日报\" --cron \"3 22 * * *\" --session main --system-event \"写今天的日报并发送给老板\" --wake now"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-code-newcli-com","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","usage":{"input":65,"output":101,"cacheRead":65382,"cacheWrite":1022,"totalTokens":66570,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773845660856}}
